&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Vivek Sagar Prasad, from Narmadapuram district of Madhya Pradesh, was part of the Indian men&amp;#39;s hockey team that won the gold medal at the Hangzhou Asian Games.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
